Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: NEXTY X COBO AIRDROP OF 300 MILLION NTY  >>> Time: From July 15 to July 19 (UTC + 7)  INSTRUCTIONS Open the Cobo Wallet app, select [My], continue to select [Tasks] to enter the Mission Center, complete task to earn CC (Note: CC is Cobo‚Äôs bonus points): - Invite 1 friend to register Cobo Cloud account, receive 300 CC, please note that you can invite many friends. - Send a minimum of 300000 NTY to Cobo Cloud, earn 10,000 CC; - Send a min of 0.0005 BTC to Cobo Cloud, earn 8000 CC; - Send a min of 0.02 ETH to Cobo Cloud, earn 8000 CC; - Send a min of 200 TRON to Cobo Cloud, earn 8000 CC; Open [My] and then select [Mall], user can convert CC into NTY, maximum 280,000 NTY; RULES - Coin storage is counted when the coin is moved from outside of Cobo Cloud to the Cobo Cloud wallet. If transferred between different Cobo Cloud accounts, it is not counted as coin storage. - For a better experience, users need to upgrade Cobo Wallet App to version 4.0 at least; (Cobo Wallet App is compatible to at least ‚ÄúiOS 9‚Ä≥ and ‚ÄúAndroid 6.0‚Äù versions) - The reward for this program is only for Cobo Cloud users, not for HD wallet users; - This program is only for Chinese and Vietnamese market users; - Cobo reserves the right to cancel rewards for users who commit fraud. COBO WALLET INSTALLATION a) Download from Cobo website: Log in to www.cobo.com, click [iOS] or [Android], scan the QR code to download: b) Download on the App Store: Open the App Store, search for [Cobo Wallet] or [Cobo], or click the link https://itunes.apple.com/app/cobo-wallet-btc-eth-more/id1406282615?mt=8, then click Download latest version; c) Download on Google Play Ôºö Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cobo.wallet Ôºå Open Google Play, search for [Cobo Wallet] or [Cobo], or click the link https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cobo.wallet, then click Download. COBO CLOUD SIGN UP STEP 1: Open Cobo Wallet, click [Register] to enter the Registration interface; STEP 2: User can use mobile number or Email to login; Mobile numbers in Vietnam may receive authentication codes more slowly, please use registered Email for more convenience; STEP 3: After entering the phone number or Email, click [Send authentication code] and check the message or Email to see if it has received the authentication code, then go back and confirm this authentication code into the Cobo app and set password; STEP 4: After installing the password, please set the PIN code. After setting the PIN code or clicking [Temporarily not setting] your Cobo cloud is successfully registered. You can now open [My], click [Mission] in Cobo App and continue to complete the mission to earn CC. Join Cobo‚Äôs telegram for more information: https://t.me/cobowallet Thanks and Best regards, ~ The Nexty & Cobo teams

Author: binhminhnguyen27197
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: Nexty Platform would like to announce that we are listing NTY/USDT on OceanEX on July 13, 2019, specifically:  Deposit + withdraw - 10:00AM July 13, UTC+8 Trading NTY/USDT -10:30AM July 14, UTC+8 About OceanEX: https://oceanex.pro (top 73 exchange on CMC)  About Nexty: Nexty is a blockchain platform specialized on payments and smart contracts. Their team is implementing the latest research on distributed systems to bring decentralization for people to have full control of their financial status, instantly and without fees. The upcoming Nexty decentralized trustless stablecoin will complete the payment solution to battle the existing fluctuation of the market on crypto payment, as well as the current decentralization problems of the existing stablecoins. Although Nexty has the convenience of a payment platform, security is the core factor of a payment network. Nexty provides ample security measure for any assets moving on the network with DCCS and a new consensus, Proof-Of-Foundation, along with verifiable delay function (VDF).

Body: And how is Proof of Foundation different than other Consensus?

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: In many replies before, I have mentioned NTF right? Well, it is a token used to choose a block sealer, only who has enough NTF that can mine the blocks. PoW choose a blocksealer by how fast a miner can seal a block right? The fastest miner will be rewarded. But in PoF, reward is given randomly to the sealer that entered the sealing round that has the number matched with the result of the calculation of the sealing round.

Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: A letter from Nexty CTO - Thanh Dao: Nexty's vision in a near future!  After a rough time in the last few days with the Nexty price, the Nexty team has made a big decision, which will be written in the letter from Nexty CTO. Please view the full letter at: https://medium.com/nextyplatform/letter-from-nexty-cto-nextys-vision-in-the-near-future-bd3652bb0900?fbclid=IwAR1S62ph3JdcOWnbTCCs6SmUm7Aw1y99APC0Y4lbKr3M7XbTqzsLrtnz6ts   Here is some highlight words we get from his letter!  "As part of the plan to bring NTY out of its current situation, we propose the following plans for the next two months:  1. Listing announcement from Oex (from 25‚Äì28th October)  2. Change smart staking rate (from 25th)  3. Working to list on Coinall ‚Äî a strategic partner with Okex so that we have chance to list on Okex (within 3 weeks to be listed on Coinall)  4. Enhance the price performance with some assistance from you in our community:  - Announcement that we need help from community to focus on Coinall and attain good trading performance on Coinall with purpose to be listed on Okex  - Announcement for the proposed 6 Billion coin burning in 11/20/2018  - preparation for the SNS campaign to attract new investors from 11/01/2018  - Assistance from community to hold the price to 0.6 won within a week (to be announced)  - Increase 7-day smart staking rate to 3% (to be announced)  - Run SNS campaign to attract more new investors (11/15/2018)  5. Find more VC to sell 10 Billion NTY ‚Äî this amount will be used for future big exchange listing, build ecosystems (November 2018 to January 2019)"  Thanks and Best regards, - The Nexty team

Having worked in software development of Smart Process Application and Document Capture solutions for over a decade, he specializes in software architectures in multiple fields ranging from enterprise solutions to open source software, from front-end UX to database cluster and embedded software architect. Taking no compromise for any trusted system, he has a great passion for a permissionless world of blockchains where trust can be given to decentralized scientific systems instead of a group of faulty individuals. Body: Can you be more informative about "Mining is exclusive for NTF holders"? How will it be?

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: NTF is created to verify and confirm NTY transactions. NTY helps to build the ecosystem. Startups increasingly use it for their transactions which lead to a growth in NTY‚Äôs value. The more NTY‚Äôs value increases, the scarcer NTF becomes and then only NTF holders have privileges to mine NTY and NTF's total supply is extremely limited: only 10,000,000.

Author: Natalie Nguyen
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: Can you tell us more about this DCCS system and what you mean by "Charge & Refund". Seems to be an interesting topic.

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: We have Dual Crytocurrency Confirmation System DCCS to process transactions. NTF which has a limit of 10,000,000 will be used to verify and confirm NTY transactions. It means that NTY transactions cost zero fee and NTF holders will receive rewards instead of verification fee.  The DCCS (Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System) will charge the receiver for an amount of NTY, then hold it for a while before issuing a refund. The more related payments are made the longer holding time is. It even takes maximum 15 - 30 days to release that fee if DCCS determine these payments as intensively continuous.

Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: How is Proof of Foundation different than other Consensus?

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: In many replies before, I have mentioned NTF right? Well, it is a token used to choose a block sealer, only who has enough NTF that can mine the blocks. PoW choose a blocksealer by how fast a miner can seal a block right? The fastest miner will be rewarded. But in PoF, reward is given randomly to the sealer that entered the sealing round that has the number matched with the result of the calculation of the sealing round.

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: Nexty introduced the Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System(DCCS) to enhance the valuation of early pNTY adopters. In addition to NTY, Nexty also has the Nexty Foundation token NTF.  DCCS processes NTY transaction without a fee instantly. NTF will be used to verify NTY transactions and owners of NTF will receive rewards at the end of each month instead of receiving immediate transaction verification fees as commonly found in other Cryptocurrencies. Moreover, only NTF holders have privileges to mine NTY and NTF‚Äôs total supply is limited to only 10,000,000.  With Nexty ecosystem model, NTY coin will increase its value, resulting in the increase of NTF‚Äôs token value as well.

Author: binhminhnguyen27197
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: Admin "#Nextyupdateüåüüåüüåü Nexty new plan for Price Stabilization   On every group and thread of Nexty, investors have strong discussion on why NTY price is not stable as stated in Nexty key features. It's true that Nexty Platform wants to create a coin that is stable enough for daily and micro transactions (starting from online and retail sales) and for E-commerce startups to raise funds via ICOs. Hence our solution is Smart Staking program functioning as a Central Bank to regulate Demand and Supply of NTY, this solution will work smoothly when Nexty community is large enough. Unfortunately, our community still remains humble and simultaneously NTY is influenced by the fluctuations of other coins, especially ETH which NTY is paired with on exchanges. We have received many suggestions like listing on new and big exchanges, but once NTY heavily depends on other high-volatility coin like ETH, finding more new exchanges is merely an ad-hoc solution. Therefore, the Nexty team has come to an important decision that supports our firm vision in the long run: to replace NTY/ETH by NTY/USDT pair. According to our plan, this new trading pairs will be listed on exchanges by August 25, 2018. When NTY is based on USDT, NTY price no longer suffers from ups and downs of the market. And Nexty team will focus our forces entirely on ecosystem expansion. " this means no longer trading NTY using ETH right???

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: Yes, we'll remove this pair to stop the dependence of NTY from a fluctuative coin like ETH

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: [Nexty annoucement] Instruction for Apps wallet data back-up and restore wallet apps   The reason for wallet back-up not an option but a must is because nexty app wallets are decentralised wallets that are directly controlled by users. Once the password is deleted, the dev cannot help recover it as the 2FA code.  I. BACK UP  #Step1: When logged in to the app, the wallet without back-up will be alerted with notification message. Click on the BACK UP button to  enter the backup page.  Or enter Setting > Backup   #Step2: In backup screen,  - After clicking ‚ÄúBACKUP‚Äù, local passcode will required to confirm BACKUP  - Successful BACKUP will then ask for file/category in your phone to save BACKUP  #Step3: Click COPY CODE to finish BACKUP process, To save the back up on Google driver, Facebook, note‚Ä¶, please click SAVE OR SHARE FILE BACKUP.  II.  RESTORE #Step1: In the home screen of the apps, please choose RESTORE WALLET  #Step2: There are 2 options: enter or attach Backup code or choose already saved BACKUP  #Step3: Select file - Choose INTERNAL STORAGE - Then choose the BACKUP file you have saved - Choose the most recent backup file - Code BACKUP will be automatically added - Enter new local passcode to restore wallet   Thanks and Best regards. - Nexty team -- Follow our social media to get more update: Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/nextycoin/ Telegram: https://t.me/nexty.io Twitter: https://twitter.com/nextyio Bitcointalk: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2498919.0 Website: https://nexty.io

Author: strelok25
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: How would you manage the payment fees to zero, is it possible? This would be great. Which platform would you use to issue the token, Ethereum or other? Tell us more about this DCCS system and what you mean by Charge & Refund. Seems to be an interesting topic. How will this protect the blockchain from spamming millions of transactions from an potential attacker?

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: We have Dual Crytocurrency Confirmation System to process transactions. NTF which has a limit of 10,000,000 will be used to verify and confirm NTY transactions. It means that NTY transactions cost zero fee and NTF holders will receive rewards instead of verification fee. NTY transactions do not require verification fee so transfers are instantly and smoothly made.  The DCCS (Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System) will charge the receiver for an amount of NTY, then hold it for a while before issuing a refund. The more related payments are made the longer holding time is. It even takes maximum 15 - 30 days to release that fee if DCCS determine these payments as intensively continuous.  Our "Charge & Refund" cycle helps to prevent spamming.

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: #Nexty update:  Today, Nexty has successfully carried out the 16th ICO within 30s.  Based on the consensus of the majority, Lending program would be canceled for the lasting and sustainable development. Instead, Smart Staking program will be officially launched on 15 January, 2018. Please bear in mind that, in order to get NTFs, investors must join Smart Staking program for at least 3 months straightly. It goes without saying that your participation is your sacred trust on us, the core value that we never take for granted. We are thankful for your support and would try our best, as a commission, to develop Nexty ecosystem to maximize benefits for our beloved investors.  One more time, only when you join Smart Staking program, can you get our cryptocurrencies named NTFs, the only coins can generate pNTYs via mining and confirming transactions. Body: Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System (DCCS), in addition to NTY, Nexty introduces other coin called NTF (Nexty Foundation).  DCCS immediately processes NTY transaction without fee. NTF will be used to verify NTY transactions and holders of NTF will receive rewards at the end of each month instead of receiving immediate transaction verification fees as commonly found in other Cryptocurrencies. Moreover, just NTF holders have privileges to mine NTY and NTF's total supply is extremely limited: only 10,000,000.  With Nexty ecosystem model, NTY coin will increase its value, resulting in the increase in NTF value.

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: The innovation is that Nexty costs no transaction fees as well as time for transaction confirmation. These procedures are obstacles to the ecommerce platform, especially in the process of micro payment and daily transactions.  Imagine if you buy a 10 cent item on Amazone and pay by Bitcoin or Ethereum. With the current exchange rate of a Bitcoin of about $10,000 and an ethereum of about $400, the payment will be extremely confusing because of too many zeroes in decimal place.  Not to mention the current high transaction costs, the payment of 10 cents by Bitcoin or Ethereum is not feasible.

Author: cpmcgrat
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: This coin seems like a good idea. But there are a few LARGE red flags for me.  1) You can deposit ETH in preparation for an ICO purchase, but the option to withdraw is greyed out/unavailable (personally deposited some to check and I cannot withdraw it). 2) The team is anonymous, easy to walk away with funds since nobody knows who they are. 3) The whitepaper contains some issues for me:     a) Lots of grammatical errors, looks like it was written in a hurry or by someone non-technical (personal red flag for me)     b) Pretty looking design, but not substantive (no real substance about what it is they do, just talks about what they would like to accomplish) 4) Most of the comments on this ANN thread are probably driven by their airdrop/bounty program here https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2560611.280  This comment will probably get buried under the "positive" press being generated, but thought I'd share my 2c anyway. Not sure about this one...

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: The innovation is that Nexty costs no transaction fees as well as time for transaction confirmation. These procedures are obstacles to the ecommerce platform, especially in the process of micro payment and daily transactions.  Imagine if you buy a 10 cent item on Amazone and pay by Bitcoin or Ethereum. With the current exchange rate of a Bitcoin of about $10,000 and an ethereum of about $400, the payment will be extremely confusing because of too many zeroes in decimal place.  Not to mention the current high transaction costs, the payment of 10 cents by Bitcoin or Ethereum is not feasible.  For details, please visit our Nextycoin

Author: Nexty.io
Title: [ANN] NextyCoin - the First Cryptocurrency: Instant Transfer with Zero Fees
Body: A Bright Future for Daily Transaction  Fast Instant Transfer  Low Zero Transfer Fees  Price Stabilization System  Website| Ann Thread | Whitepaper| Twitter| Facebook| Telegram | Blog | FAQ  ANN thread in other languages: Russian   Airdrop & Bounty Program  What is Nexty   Nexty is a Fintech ecosystem which helps e-commerce and technology startups to raise funds from community. Nexty itself has a cryptocurrency named NTY with various dominant features such as Instant Transfer, Zero Transfer Fees, Price Stabilisation System, and Dual Crypto Currency   The Problems    Cryptocurrency has been drawing a lot of attention recently, although it is evaluated to be the solution of the above backlog but has not really solved these problems. Some Cryptocurrencies has reduced international settlement time to near-instantaneous threshold, but soon after it becomes slow when the number of users increased dramatically. In addition, payment fees are relatively high, even some types have higher costs using old payment methods such as online credit card, online payment system...   Average Transaction Time in 2017 (blockchain.info)   Average Transaction Value in 2017 (bitinfocharts.com)   Average Transaction Fees in 2017 (bitinfocharts.com)    HOW IT WORKS   Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System includes two types of Cryptocurrency operating in parallel. The former called NTY, is the main cryptocurrency for using in daily transactions. The latter called NTF, is for transaction confirmation system. Transaction confirmation system is built on a peer-to-peer network with specific criteria to meet operational requirements. The breakthrough here is that instead of charging per transaction, those who are the holders of the second type of cryptocurrency will be rewarded with a small amount of cryptocurrency at the minor rate at the end of each month and this will allow the transaction fees to be zero while still guaranteeing the benefits to the persons who contribute to transaction confirmation system.   ROADMAP   Benefits for Investors Be part of Nexty Foundation with NTF bonus which is rare Mining is exclusive for NTF holders Lifetime  earnings NTY from DCCS  by POF Lifetime  earnings from annual profit generated by Price Stabilisation  System Get NTY when it is still affordable Various ways to get profits from our kickstart programs: Smart Staking, Affiliates... Frequently Asked Questions  1. What is Nexty?  Nexty is a platform based on blockchain technology to help the e-commercial startups to raise funds from community. The startups themselves would create the ecosystem for Nexty.   2. Is it possible for startups outside of e-commercial field to raise funds?   Totally possible! However, startups in this field would benefit more from Nexty ecosystem, especially the advantages of Instant Transfer and Zero Fee technologies of Nexty.  3. What are Instant Transfer and Zero Fees?  These unique technologies are exclusive to Nexty, providing ecommercial startups namely online shops, online service with much effective transactions and greater advantages for users. How amazing and convenient it is to shop and pay online without transaction fees or transaction confirmation!  For more information of such technologies, please consult our    Whitepaper.   4. Many platforms are functioning the same as Nexty like Ethereum, Neo, Wave, etc‚Ä¶ What makes Nexty different?   The innovation is that Nexty costs no transaction fees as well as time for transaction confirmation. These procedures are obstacles to the ecommerce platform, especially in the process of micro payment and daily transactions.  Imagine if you buy a 10 cent item on Amazone and pay by Bitcoin or Ethereum. With the current exchange rate of a Bitcoin of about $10,000 and an ethereum of about $400, the payment will be extremely confusing because of too many zeroes in decimal place.  Not to mention the current high transaction costs, the payment of 10 cents by Bitcoin or Ethereum is not feasible.   5. Considering all above-mentioned advantages, total supply of Nexty should be huge enough, at least exceed the initial amount of 22,000,000?   22,000,000 is the initial total supply of pNTY. 1 pNTY=10,000 NTY.   6. Hence, the total initial supply of Nexty is 220 billion. Does such a huge amount devalue Nexty?   It is true that Nexty starts with 220,000,000,000 NTY, resulting in the conversion of 10,000 NTY to 1 pNTY. pNTY is used for transaction of Crypto currencies, while NTY is used for daily transactions on e-commercial businesses.  Additionally, Nexty also possesses other systems called Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System to boost the benefit and value of early pNTY owners.  7. What is Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System?  Dual Cryptocurrency Confirmation System (DCCS), in addition to NTY, Nexty introduces other coin called NTF (Nexty Foundation).  DCCS immediately processes NTY transaction without fee. NTF will be used to verify NTY transactions and holders of NTF will receive rewards at the end of each month instead of receiving immediate transaction verification fees as commonly found in other Cryptocurrencies. Moreover, just NTF holders have privileges to mine NTY and NTF's total supply is extremely limited: only 10,000,000.  With Nexty ecosystem model, NTY coin will increase its value, resulting in the increase in NTF value.  8. How to possess the NTF coins?  The privilege rate for the earliest 10,000,000 pNTY owners is that 1 pNTY gets 1 NTF, which means purchasing one, earning double. This means that you only have the opportunity to own NTF during the ICO period; otherwise, you can only purchase this coin once it is introduced on the trading platform.  However, the purchasing possibility is low because NTF owners can mine NTY coins and obtain NTY by Proof of Foundation algorithm. Because of such benefits, NTF holders will not sell the NTFs they hold, or sell at high price. The current price of Ethereum is over $400, the target price of 1 pNTY will be $300 at the end of 2018.  The owners of 10,000,000 pNTY must, firstly, freeze their pNTYs to receive NTFs through the Smart Staking program.   9. What is Smart Staking? Once frozen, the NTY coins would stop generating profits?   Actually the term of ‚Äúfrozen‚Äù or ‚Äúfreeze‚Äù is not a worry. Frozen by Smart Staking program even offers you greater benefit.  Smart Staking means no online mode for maintenance as Staking normally but still earns increment. For more detailed Smart Staking program, consult here  10. How to join ICO?   prequisite condition is to have Nexty account. If you do not have one,    sign up here.  Once you have an account, log in here and load Bitcoin or Ethereum then wait for the ICO sale date. See ICO sale date here.  11. Is Affiliate program available in Nexty?  Sure, each successful referral will generate 6% commission on purchased amount of pNTY  12. Why is Nexty's affiliate program different from most of other projects?  I see the 1st level commission of other projects is usually the highest.  Nexty targets a strong and sustainable community, so we created this affiliate system so that referrals are responsible for helping and guiding whoever they refer if they want to get the most from this affiliate program.  13. With such an affiliate program structure, doesn‚Äôt Nexty worry that people themselves create multiple accounts? Is it possible for a user to create multiple accounts?  For the best identification, each user is allowed to create one account only.  Nexty will strictly manage this issue and lock the offending accounts. Consult the Terms of Use for details.  14. How many coins per person can be owned during the ICO?  The Minimum amount: 100 pNTY The Maximum amount: 500 pNTY  15. What kind of load accepted by Nexty?  Nexty accepts Bitcoin and Ethereum  16. Can I withdraw despite the load?  In order to maintain the system and avoid overload, during the ICO period, the withdrawal function is temporarily disabled. You can withdraw when ICO ends or your purchase succeeds.  17. Can I transfer my pNTY internally to another member?  Totally possible but you are highly advised of raising alert of security!   18. Please follow these instructions to enable double layer security for your account:     Step 1: Sign in to your Nexty account here. Step 2: Click on Two Factor Authentication in the avatar at the top right corner of your account. You will set up 2-layer security.  20. With such limited amount in open sales, I am afraid I will not buy pNTY in the ICO period  To ensure fairness for all members, Nexty only allows one account to purchase a maximum of 500 pNTY. Those who have purchased a full limit of 500 pNTY will not be able to purchase more and we will handle it tightly. Your luck plays important roles in this case.  21. Where can I see Nexty Roadmap and Whitepaper?  Click here for Roadmap  Click here for    Whitepaper    22. How the Startup would be invested by Nexty?  Many Start-ups develop great ideas and even create completed products, but are lacking in finance to develop the project. Hence, Nexty will invest in such Startups by providing a platform to raise funds through the ICO and support communications as well as strategy advice, in return Nexty will receive a percentage of the shares under the deal in that startup.  Once an ICO is created on the basis of Nexty, investors have to buy Token via pNTY, which creates tremendous growth potential and elevates the value of the NTY.  Any more questions you may have, contact us through mailto:support@nexty.io
